ation (the HDF-N and GWS) produced significant detections\nin each. The detection in the HDF-N gives an X-ray derived SFR of 42.4+/-7.8\nMsolar/yr per LBG and, by comparing with the UV SFR, the implied UV extinction\ncorrection is 4.1+/-0.8. (abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Sep 2006 20:10:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
