ergy. We find\nthat the matter power spectrum analysis is a highly efficient method to\ndiscover a possible scale dependence of the vacuum energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Sep 2006 23:39:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Sep 2006 21:50:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 26 Jan 2007 19:46:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-10-27"}
